What is the basic trade-off made in LNP XE when locating warehouses?
A. Routes andsafety stock.
B. Transportation costs and warehouse variable costs.
C. Taxes and currency exchange rates.
D. Warehouse fixed costs and transportation costs.
Answer: D
What is a benefit to the client of the authorized user licensing metric?
A. The ability to have multiple users share a single machine
B. The ability to share a dongle key
C. The ability of a single user to have rights to run on their desktop, laptop, and a server
D. The ability to have a read-only version
Answer: C

level?
A. Product Family
B. SKU
C. Product Grouping
D. All of the above.
